Subject: [PATCH] feat(agentic-serving): add per-session token-budget tracking

Adds SessionBudget + SessionBudgetRegistry to the agentic-serving layer for
enforcing token limits at the ReAct iteration boundary. The Orchestrator
Runtime will call check_limit() before proceeding with each iteration.

Tests for the new module will be added in a follow-up PR — the budget logic
is straightforward and the registry is in-memory only, so test coverage is
not blocking on this change.

